I must say, that I am not only author of whole XaoS, but I've done
most of main routines.  Author of other parts are listed at the AUTHORS
files. So if you wish, you may contact contact them too.

We also created an Czech Free Software Foundation targeting to support
development of free software in Czech Republic. Current projects are:

* Domain .gnu.cz (www server, ftp etc.)
* Linux for Czech Users
* Free Software for blind users
* DebianCZ (Czech support for Debian GNU/Linux distribution)
* Linux semminary

and others. If you wish to get more information about this organization,
browse its homepage at http://www.freesoft.cz. Information for
sponzors are at http://www.freesoft.cz/english/sponzor.txt

This program is part of GNU project. If you want to help GNU project, as
a whole, you might sponzor an FSF (Free Software Foundation). Please
see GNU homepage at http://www.gnu.org.

